```scene step=7 narration="Recap: one CH₄ plus two O₂ yields one CO₂ plus two H₂O. Atoms conserved; bonds in hydrocarbon + O=O are replaced by stronger C=O and O-H bonds, releasing ~890 kJ/mol." code_lines=14-15
{ "primitives": [
